items.sentence: My younger brother is still in elementary school.
Tom came over to my desk to give something to me.
Be careful what you wish for. It might come true.
I saw Tom and his father walking down the street.
I don't yet know how much money Tom will lend me.
I don't yet know how much money Tom will give me.
I didn't know why Tom wasn't supposed to do that.
I didn't approve of the way Tom was doing things.
All I know is that Tom is a boy at Mary's school.
After Tom broke up with Mary, he joined the army.
